data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE Feb 3rd 11 am - 2 pm*** Charming single-story brick home in Harbour Woods, featuring majestic oaks and close to St. John's River boat ramp. This spacious residence boasts a large great room with a fireplace, a separate dining area, a family room, and hardwood flooring. The updated primary suite includes a stunning bath with a tiled walk-in shower with rain head, dual vanities, and a walk-in closet. It also offers three additional bedrooms, each with their own baths and closets. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, wood-grain tile flooring, stainless appliances, a breakfast nook, and ample storage. The private backyard is an entertainer's dream, complete with a large brick patio, a sparkling pool and spa, and a vast, fully fenced lawn. 2019 ROOF! Ask about available Assumable VA Loan for those who qualify.
